      "content": "That's a good start. Can you go deeper into the \"marketplace of ideas\" part? Like, specifically how does government intervention like content moderation laws or age verification requirements actually break that marketplace? I want to make sure my post shows why these aren't just \"rules\" but actual damage to the philosophy of free speech.",
